.DS_Store
node_modules/

# Private feature specs — kept LOCAL, never pushed to the public repo.
# Convention: put the word "private" anywhere in the filename and it stays
# untracked. Use for personal/unofficial-API features that don't belong in the
# published spec set. These must be self-contained (do NOT add rows for them to
# the tracked MENU.md / DEPENDENCIES.md, or the name would leak). Track them in
# the gitignored MENU.private.md / DEPENDENCIES.private.md instead.
*private*.md
features/*private*.md
prompts/*private*.md
MENU.private.md
DEPENDENCIES.private.md
